16:42.740 --> 16:44.351
some more responsibility.

16:44.394 --> 16:45.961
And time for you to start

16:46.005 --> 16:47.441
thinking about your future.

16:47.484 --> 16:49.138
I have been thinking
about my future.

16:49.182 --> 16:51.140
And I've actually been
meaning to tell you.

16:51.184 --> 16:53.316
There's a woman
I've been seeing.

16:53.360 --> 16:54.709
A woman?

16:54.752 --> 16:56.276
Who's her family?

16:56.319 --> 16:58.104
She's not...

16:58.147 --> 17:00.236
she's not a part
of the faith.

17:00.280 --> 17:01.977
But I love her
and I think if you just...

17:02.021 --> 17:03.022
Son...

17:03.065 --> 17:04.893
you're young.

17:04.936 --> 17:07.287
And you want to sow
some wild oats.

17:07.330 --> 17:09.071
And that's all right.

17:09.115 --> 17:10.638
The Lord understands
your need for comfort.

17:10.681 --> 17:12.074
But...

17:12.118 --> 17:14.555
all this will be yours someday.

17:14.598 --> 17:16.992
You're gonna need
to find someone

17:17.036 --> 17:19.429
