your needs

17:21.431 --> 17:22.824
and the life you must lead.

17:22.867 --> 17:25.957
But I don't need
all of this to serve the Lord.

17:26.001 --> 17:27.568
These people,
they're pouring

17:27.611 --> 17:28.960
out their money.

17:29.004 --> 17:30.614
That ring on your finger

17:30.658 --> 17:34.053
