17:38.666 --> 17:41.321
It's ordained.

17:41.364 --> 17:44.933
This ring reminds me
of who I am.

17:44.976 --> 17:47.109
This is how we praise Him.

17:47.153 --> 17:49.546
This is all

17:49.590 --> 17:51.374
in Jesus' name.

17:51.418 --> 17:53.072
Hmm?

17:54.638 --> 17:55.857
Yes, sir.
All right.

17:55.900 --> 17:57.989
Amen.Amen.

