18:57.048 --> 18:58.833
You know?

18:58.876 --> 19:00.356
And I want to know
what happened.

19:00.400 --> 19:02.315
She doesn't even know.

19:02.358 --> 19:04.186
And until we have
more information,

19:04.230 --> 19:06.188
it's just not safe to see her.

19:06.232 --> 19:08.886
But, Dad...Mariah... I mean it.

19:10.018 --> 19:12.455
This conversation is
closed for now.

